    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "This potent weapon used by Treerazer is a *+4 greater corrosive major striking obsidian greataxe* that grants a +4 item bonus to attack rolls, deals an extra 2d6 damage to plants, and has the properties of adamantine. It deals an additional die of damage when wielded by Treerazer.",
